ips, i.e. posting the remaining\ninventory in the dark pool at every point in time, are not necessarily\nbeneficial.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 May 2014 17:11:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Jan 2015 09:37:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2015 15:32:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2016 13:26:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-13"}
