 the\nlattice potential, say, scalar product with a function, integration or\ndifferentiation, which can be performed easily in tensor arithmetics on large\n3D grids with 1D cost. Numerical tests illustrate the performance of the tensor\nsummation method and confirm the estimated bounds on the tensor ranks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 May 2014 15:45:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Mar 2015 17:49:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
